{
  "name": "Greater Restoration",
  "_id": "matSplGreaterRes",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You touch a creature and magically remove one of the following effects from it:</p><ul><li>1 &amp;Reference[Exhaustion] level</li><li>The &amp;Reference[Charmed], &amp;Reference[Petrified], &amp;Reference[Possessed], or &amp;Reference[Weakened] condition</li><li>A curse, including the target's Attunement to a cursed magic item</li><li>Any reduction to one of the target's ability scores</li><li>Any reduction to the target's Hit Point maximum</li></ul><p><strong>Using a Higher-Level Spell Slot.</strong> The range increases with a spell slot of level 6-7 (30 feet), or 8+ (60 feet).</p>",
